interactivity.requirements: 20 Yumi Affection You must have seen or permanently missed the following Events: Seen " Snake Venom " from Tsuneyo Tojo Seen " Apples to Apples " from Yumi Yamaguchi
interactivity.to_get_this_event: Visit Yumi at the City Streets after all Requirements have been fulfilled.

progression.synopsis: Yumi is having a pizza with Sensei and complaining about how the cafe didn't appreciate her dedicated approach . They talk about what to do next in her job hunt, and Sensei suggests trying Tojo Ramen. She agrees, and says that she'll try to seem more "normal" this time.

changelog: This Event was added in Update 0.9p1.
